 for the change in food consumption. Since the question (or investigation) involved the situations before and after the 
 families had entered the phone services business, 
 (understanding/ explanation) of the responses depends on the ceteris 
 paribus idea (you think is true). In order to test this fully, 
 however, further research on consumption effects is 
 needed. 
